Package: piccr
Title: Correct and Calibrate Picarro CRDS Stable Isotope Data.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Muench", email = "thomas.muench@awi.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This R package implements a method to correct and calibrate the
     raw stable isotopologue data of water measured by Picarro Inc. cavity
     ring-down spectroscopy measurement devices.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.1)
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests:
    testthat,
    covr,
    devtools
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports:
    yaml,
    tidyverse
URL: https://github.com/EarthSystemDiagnostics/piccr
BugReports: https://github.com/EarthSystemDiagnostics/piccr/issues
